Hi everyone! Here it is was I suggest to people who have a combination skin. But let’s see all the products:

paulaschoice Hydrating Gel-To-Cream Cleanser✨
I chose this gentle cleanser in order to hydrate those dry areas of combination skin, but let’s not forget that hydration is important in all skin types.

imfrom_global Rice Toner✨
This toner is super viral and for a reason: it helps so much strengthening skin barrier and achieving that “glass skin” that is popular in Korea.

numbuzin_global Skin Softening Serum 3✨
This product is the most famous by Numbuzin. As the rice toner, this one helps to improve skin texture and to achieve an healthier skin. 

skin1004official Soothing Cream✨
I own this moisturizer and it has the perfect texture for combination skin: the gel texture is perfect for oily areas, so the result is not greasy or heavy over the skin, but at the same time it hydrates dry areas. 

beautyofjoseon_official Sunscreen✨
As I always say, this sunscreen is perfect for dry skin, it’s very moisturizing, but for oily skin sometimes it can be heavy if you put a moisturizer too. So if you have a combination skin this one could be the right one for you. A solution could be to wear a moisturizer + sunscreen on dry areas, and only sunscreen on oily areas, so your skincare is well balanced.
